data.description: Discover contemporary elegance in this 3-bedroom, 2-bath home on a coveted corner lot. The master bedroom boasts a private patio exit, while the en-suite bath with a tile shower and dual vanities. Enjoy the modern touches of granite countertops, vaulted ceilings, and hardwood floors. Cozy up by the masonry fireplace in the open living area. Plus, all appliances are included for your convenience. This is your chance to own a stylish, move-in-ready gem. Don't miss out—schedule a viewing today and experience the perfect blend of comfort and sophistication.
